9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"A Fistful of Dollars | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The Man With No Name enters the Mexican village of San Miguel in the midst of a power struggle among the three Rojo brothers and sheriff John Baxter. When a regiment of Mexican soldiers bearing gold intended to pay for new weapons is waylaid by the Rojo brothers, the stranger inserts himself into the middle of the long-simmering battle, selling false information to both sides for his own benefit."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148177/a-fistful-of-dollars"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"A Fistful of Dollars"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"The Man With No Name enters the Mexican village of San Miguel in the midst of a power struggle among the three Rojo brothers and sheriff John Baxter. When a regiment of Mexican soldiers bearing gold intended to pay for new weapons is waylaid by the Rojo brothers, the stranger inserts himself into the middle of the long-simmering battle, selling false information to both sides for his own benefit."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148177/a-fistful-of-dollars"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lBwOEpwVeUAmrmglcstnaGcJq3Y.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"A Fistful of Dollars"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"The Man With No Name enters the Mexican village of San Miguel in the midst of a power struggle among the three Rojo brothers and 